                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">El Paso</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-01-11T14:00:00-07:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 11, 1916, 2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Murder of Watson and companions confirmed. An American of the party, name
                    unknown, escaped and reported facts.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cobb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
